TRACEROUTE (TRACERT) TO www.youtube.com

Objective:
Find the network path (hops) from your computer to www.youtube.com.

On Windows:
1. Open Command Prompt.
2. Type:
   tracert www.youtube.com
3. Press Enter.
4. Wait for the trace to complete.

On macOS/Linux:
1. Open Terminal.
2. Type:
   traceroute www.youtube.com
3. Press Enter.

